    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "I'm still confused as to why the spawnpoint actor is using the `SpiceBloom` trait.  The whole purpose of the trait is to spawn spice when the bloom is killed, but the spawnpoint then hacks around that by making itself uncrushable and unkillable.  Can we please use a more suitable trait to replace the spawn point with the bloom after the warmup delay?"
  },
