    "body": "You could avoid the new trait by adding a `Duration` field to the `GrantCondition` trait, and then have `KillsSelf` trigger when that condition is removed.\r\n\r\nThe new conditions logic works properly during actor creation, so you shouldn't have to worry about `KillsSelf` triggering before the condition is first applied."
